      <title>Angular–i18n : ngx-translate的应用</title>
      <link href="/2022/07/09/angular-translate/"/>
      <url>/2022/07/09/angular-translate/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="translate在angular中的应用"><a href="#translate在angular中的应用" class="headerlink" title="translate在angular中的应用"></a>translate在angular中的应用</h1><h2 id="1-1-translate常量在HTML中的基础应用"><a href="#1-1-translate常量在HTML中的基础应用" class="headerlink" title="1.1 translate常量在HTML中的基础应用"></a>1.1 translate常量在HTML中的基础应用</h2><p>component.html</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">&#123;&#123; &#39;常量&#39; | translate &#125;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>在HTML标签中属性的translate</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">placeholder&#x3D;&quot;&#123;&#123; &#39;ReqDescNote&#39; | translate &#125;&#125;&quot;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="1-2-translate变量在HTML中的基础应用"><a href="#1-2-translate变量在HTML中的基础应用" class="headerlink" title="1.2 translate变量在HTML中的基础应用"></a>1.2 translate变量在HTML中的基础应用</h2><p>component.html</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">&#123;&#123; 变量名 | translate &#125;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>在HTML标签中属性的translate</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">placeholder&#x3D;&quot;&#123;&#123; ReqDescNote | translate &#125;&#125;&quot;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="1-3-translate在HTML的breadcrumb中的应用"><a href="#1-3-translate在HTML的breadcrumb中的应用" class="headerlink" title="1.3 translate在HTML的breadcrumb中的应用"></a>1.3 translate在HTML的breadcrumb中的应用</h2><p>layout.componnet.html</p><pre class="line-numbers language-HTML" data-language="HTML"><code class="language-HTML">&lt;nz-breadcrumb [nzAutoGenerate]&#x3D;&quot;true&quot; [nzRouteLabel]&#x3D;&quot;&#39;breadcrumbI18nKey&#39;&quot; [nzRouteLabelFn]&#x3D;&quot;translateFn&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;nz-breadcrumb&gt;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>layout-routing.module.ts</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">&#123;  path: &#39;engineeringapplication&#39;,  canActivate: [AuthGuard],  canActivateChild: [AuthGuard],  data: &#123; breadcrumbI18nKey: &#39;EngineeringApplication&#39; &#125;,&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>i18N–&gt;en.json</p><pre class="line-numbers language-json" data-language="json"><code class="language-json">&#123;  &quot;EngineeringApplication&quot;: &quot;Engineering Application&quot;,&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>i18N–&gt;zh.json</p><pre class="line-numbers language-json" data-language="json"><code class="language-json">&#123;  &quot;EngineeringApplication&quot;: &quot;单据申请&quot;,&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>layout.component.ts</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">translateFn &#x3D; (key: string) &#x3D;&gt; &#123;  let translateValue &#x3D; &#39;&#39;;  if (!!key) &#123;    translateValue &#x3D; this.translateService.instant(key);  &#125;  return translateValue;&#125;;constructor(  private translateService: TranslateService,) &#123; &#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="1-4-translate在constants中的应用"><a href="#1-4-translate在constants中的应用" class="headerlink" title="1.4 translate在constants中的应用"></a>1.4 translate在constants中的应用</h2><h3 id="1-4-1-Before"><a href="#1-4-1-Before" class="headerlink" title="1.4.1 Before"></a>1.4.1 Before</h3><p>constants.ts</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">export const INVOICES_APPLICYION_ITEMS: FormItem[] &#x3D; [  &#123; text: &#39;区域&#39;, value: &quot;area&quot;, style: &quot;&quot; &#125;,  &#123; text: &#39;建筑名称&#39;, value: &quot;building&quot;, style: &quot;&quot; &#125;,  &#123; text: &#39;楼层&#39;, value: &quot;floor&quot;, style: &quot;&quot; &#125;]<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>component.ts</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">formItems &#x3D; [...INVOICES_APPLICYION_ITEMS];<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>component.html</p><pre class="line-numbers language-HTML" data-language="HTML"><code class="language-HTML">&lt;nz-list nzBordered&gt;  &lt;nz-list-item *ngFor&#x3D;&quot;let item of formItems&quot;&gt;    &lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;content-name&quot;&gt;&lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;start&quot;&gt;*&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&#123;&#123; item.text &#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;  &lt;&#x2F;nz-list-item&gt;&lt;&#x2F;nz-list&gt;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="1-4-2-After"><a href="#1-4-2-After" class="headerlink" title="1.4.2 After"></a>1.4.2 After</h3><p>i18N–&gt;en.json</p><pre class="line-numbers language-json" data-language="json"><code class="language-json">&#123;  &quot;Area&quot;: &quot;Area&quot;,  &quot;Building&quot;: &quot;Building&quot;,  &quot;Floor&quot;: &quot;Floor&quot;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>i18N–&gt;zh.json</p><pre class="line-numbers language-json" data-language="json"><code class="language-json">&#123;  &quot;Area&quot;: &quot;区域&quot;,  &quot;Building&quot;: &quot;建筑名称&quot;,  &quot;Floor&quot;: &quot;楼层&quot;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>constants.ts</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">export const INVOICES_APPLICYION_ITEMS: FormItem[] &#x3D; [  &#123; text: &#39;Area&#39;, value: &quot;area&quot;, style: &quot;&quot; &#125;,  &#123; text: &#39;Building&#39;, value: &quot;building&quot;, style: &quot;&quot; &#125;,  &#123; text: &#39;Floor&#39;, value: &quot;floor&quot;, style: &quot;&quot; &#125;]<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>component.ts</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">formItems &#x3D; [...INVOICES_APPLICYION_ITEMS];<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>component.html</p><pre class="line-numbers language-HTML" data-language="HTML"><code class="language-HTML">&lt;nz-list nzBordered&gt;  &lt;nz-list-item *ngFor&#x3D;&quot;let item of formItems&quot;&gt;    &lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;content-name&quot;&gt;&lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;start&quot;&gt;*&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&#123;&#123; item.text | translate &#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;  &lt;&#x2F;nz-list-item&gt;&lt;&#x2F;nz-list&gt;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="1-5-translate在component-ts中的使用"><a href="#1-5-translate在component-ts中的使用" class="headerlink" title="1.5 translate在component.ts中的使用"></a>1.5 translate在component.ts中的使用</h2><p>i18N–&gt;en.json</p><pre class="line-numbers language-json" data-language="json"><code class="language-json">&#123;  &quot;Area&quot;: &quot;Area&quot;,  &quot;Building&quot;: &quot;Building&quot;,  &quot;Floor&quot;: &quot;Floor&quot;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>i18N–&gt;zh.json</p><pre class="line-numbers language-json" data-language="json"><code class="language-json">&#123;  &quot;Area&quot;: &quot;区域&quot;,  &quot;Building&quot;: &quot;建筑名称&quot;,  &quot;Floor&quot;: &quot;楼层&quot;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>component.ts</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">area &#x3D; this.translateService.instant(&#39;Area&#39;);constructor(  private translateService:TranslateService) &#123; &#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
